type: software
title: "EvalBot — Automated Teaching Evaluation Form Filler"
abstract: >-
  An agent-driven tool that automates medical teaching evaluation forms.
  A Python CLI handles HTTP/HTML parsing while Claude Code generates
  contextually appropriate feedback in Traditional Chinese. Designed as
  a reusable pattern for any hospital's web-based evaluation system.
